citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:00am-10:30pm
on 18-APR-23. Inspector called numbers on file with no answer, left message. Knocked on door, left flyer. Insepctor
waited 30 minutes and attempted to call again with no answer. Inspector left site.
End Section
